item.title: dropout笔记
item.author: wangke
item.description: 原理 dropout原理, 随机丢弃一些(输入)神经元, 防止参数过拟合 Applies Dropout to the input. Dropout consists in randomly setting a fraction rate of input units to 0 at each update during training time, which helps prevent overfitting. The units that are kept are scaled by 1
